{"tid":576882,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[八年分手] 我真係好掛住個ex..","createTime":"2018-03-01T09:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T09:59:21.000Z","uid":164837,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d5321b5e1f4a617b7c8d715aa9528f2f82ad70ce","tid":576882,"uid":164837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"分左手差唔多半年啦...<br />\n<br />\n轉眼間同我分左手後佢已經成為左別人的另一半<br />\n<br />\n我仲每分每秒掛住緊佢。<br />\n<br />\n同我來說佢就係好似屋企人一樣...亦係我第一個女朋友...<br />\n<br />\n我真係好後悔以往太take it for granted..<br />\n<br />\n天啊...我可以點move on...仲可以點重頭拍拖鐘意番人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但最後只可以怪自己。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9 up完畢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e6b0ea2f17dcb7c219f3e329e872329c22bfdf","tid":576882,"uid":15419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:27:25.000Z","msg":"一齊咗八年, 分手無耐就可以同其他人一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad7103773279a1ad9936384c615931d42c18c79","tid":576882,"uid":164837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"32e6b0ea2f17dcb7c219f3e329e872329c22bfdf","tid":576882,"uid":15419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:27:25.000Z","msg":"一齊咗八年, 分手無耐就可以同其他人一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:29:43.000Z","msg":"係同我分手之後立刻同第個一齊<br />\n<br />\n因為當時我係外國讀書，而佢之前應該同朋友落bar識既<br />\n<br />\n個男仔應該追佢<br />\n<br />\n我而家番黎香港咩都無了 <br />\n<br />\n好似無左個家人一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3e8fade6bfedf505e247a098c99670db513e27","tid":576882,"uid":15419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s